title: The Dark Side of Oz DVD
description: Call it The Darkside of the Rainbow or whatever, but this DVD is my favorite version. The higher quality video and audio rips combined with interesting dvd menus make this a lot better than the other versions around. You can watch the full movie and toggle between 3 audio tracks: the original Wizard of Oz audio, the Dark Side of the Moon, or both. It also has a scene selection, so you can jump to a specific chapter if you want.
